# .amp — j4flmao/skills

Amazon Q Developer. Rules load by glob match.

## Compress (ALWAYS)
Strip: a/an/the | just/really | sure/happy | I think/might be | however/moreover | code explain | preamble/postamble
Pattern: `[thing] [action] [why]. [next].`
Full prose: security. destructive.

## Routing
No match → `skills/core/master-orchestrator/SKILL.md`. Detect stack then route.
Phase order: planning → backend → frontend → mobile → dev-loop → devops → management.

